Llama Lords is a gaming clan, we play CSS, WoW, TF2 and more.
Please play on our Gun Game server
83.142.230.77:27015

Tag Towers is another fun map idea by Lord Azael: the map is basically the [LL] tags! Shed any thoughts of bad quality due to designs based around the tag and not gameplay - this map has been carefully made to keep gameplay interesting and, at the same time, display [LL] to the gods. It's a small map good for anything from 2 to 10 players.

For those curious as to the whereabouts of version 1, it was never released (but was tested on our server publicly). This was due to a water texture error.


Please visit the clan website www.llamalords.co.uk
We are not recruiting at the moment, however social and regular server players are usually welcome to join!
This map can be uploaded to other download portals if needs be.
Ask my permission before editing or decompiling the map.
Steam Friends: explosivose

LL ftw ^_^
